### [3 Kings (1 Kings) Chapter 3](../../../bib/kjv/kg1003.htm#001.md)

[3 Kings (1 Kings)](../../../bib/kjv/kg1001.htm#001.md)

<span class="margnote"><span id="an_000">kg1 3:0</span></span>

Overview

[Kg1 3:1](../../../bib/kjv/kg1003.htm#001.md), Solomon marries Pharaoh's
daughter; [Kg1 3:2](../../../bib/kjv/kg1003.htm#002.md), High places being
in use, Solomon sacrifices at Gibeon; [Kg1
3:5](../../../bib/kjv/kg1003.htm#005.md), Solomon at Gibeon, in the choice
which God gave him, preferring wisdom, obtains wisdom, riches, and
honour; [Kg1 3:16](../../../bib/kjv/kg1003.htm#016.md), Solomon's judgment
makes him renowned.

